# RECOMMENDED — single key, production-equivalent asymmetric LLM assignment.
# Routes each role to its architecture-spec model (Qwen3 Max trader, DeepSeek
# V4 technical analyst, Gemini 2.5 Pro fundamentals, GPT-5.2 news, Claude
# Sonnet 4.6 risk/bull/bear/fund-manager, Claude Haiku 4.5 sentiment, Llama
# 3.3 70B reflection) through OpenRouter.
